Heat grill to medium heat. Shape meat into 6 (1/2-inch-thick) patties. Grill 4 to 5 min. on each side or until done (160 degrees F). Meanwhile, microwave VELVEETA and RO*TEL in microwaveable bowl on HIGH 5 min. or until VELVEETA is completely melted, stirring after 3 min. Place burgers on bottom halves of buns; top each with 2 Tbsp. VELVEETA sauce. Cover with lettuce, tomatoes and tops of buns.